Version 0.2.0 (2011-05-18)
--------------------------
- Strike alerts (SMS, E-Mail, URL)
  New constants added: BO_ALERTS, BO_SMS_GATEWAY_URL
- New user levels
- import improvements
- main map has now own width/height (you have to use the '!important' tag to change size!)


